shape: sequence_diagram

Developer: SaaS Developer
API: Management API
DB: Data Store
Cache: In-Memory Route Cache (Gateway)

Developer -> API: 1. Submit OpenAPI Payload
API -> API: 2. Parse & Validate OAS 3.0+ Schema
API -> API: 3. Extract Paths, Methods, and Security Scopes
API -> DB: 4. Persist Tenant Route Rules
DB -> API: 5. Confirm Transaction
API -> Cache: 6. Push Update Event (Invalidate/Refresh)
Cache -> API: 7. Acknowledge Sync
API -> Developer: 8. Return 200 OK & Parsed Rule Summary
